achine/Live+&+Rare\">Read more on Last.fm</a>.","content":"Live & Rare is a live/compilation  album by Rage Against the Machine, released in Japan on June 30, 1998 by Sony Music Japan and only available overseas as an import. It comprises \"official bootlegs\" previously available on other singles as well as a pair of tracks from the band's 1991 demo. It was released internationally on digital streaming platforms in early 2022. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Rage+Against+the+Machine/Live+&+Rare\">Read more on Last.fm</a>. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply."}}}